column4: Fix some bugs of AI and delete useless code

[added] methods to TextField to set the selection and cursor position. [fixed] f'ing bug in gdx2d.c. I hate myself and i want to die. Updated natives.  git-svn-id: https://libgdx.googlecode.com/svn/trunk@2793 6c4fd544-2939-11df-bb46-9574ba5d0bfa

It compiles!  Fixed a lot of compilation errors related to the modifications to the latest version of libgdx Implemented the actions and base scene2d  fixed compilation issues. I'm sensing some leaks  though.
Implemented ShapeRenderer and the new Box2DDebugRenderer  - Also updated Box2D to the latest version (2.0.1) - Fixed all tests so they worl again (hurray!)

[updated] Util maps  added get with default value. [updated] Interpolation  added bounce constructors. [updated] SoundTest  use volume to start playback. [fixed] OpenAL crash  issue 551. Fixed Bug: loopDuration could be wrong  The loopDuration could be higher than the sum of all durations when the float had more than 3 decimal places.
fixed bug

Bugfix for AnimationController  When an animation has 0 seconds duration (it's still  not moving) the AnimationDesc.update() would hang indefinitely. This should make each frame consume 1 loop  though I'm not sure if this is the best way to handle this. What do you guys think?
